          "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Stored in the spleen and absorbed in the intestine by albumin</span></span></span></p>"
